&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Conclusions:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(I) Some stars are ribbons.&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; &lt;strong&gt;Follows&lt;/strong&gt; (As,&amp;nbsp;Some stars are buttons and&amp;nbsp;All buttons are ribbons, which implies that s&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;ome stars are ribbons)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(II) Some ribbons are buttons.&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;rarr;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;&quot;&gt;Follows&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;(As,&amp;nbsp;All buttons are ribbons, it implies that some ribbons are buttons)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, &amp;lsquo;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;Both conclusions (I) and (II) follow&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;rsquo; is the correct answer.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;न्यूनतम संभावित वेन आरेख निम्नलिखित है: &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

